{#
NovaSight ClickHouse Dictionary Template
==========================================

Creates a ClickHouse dictionary for dimension lookups.

Template Variables:
- dict_name: Name of the dictionary (required)
- database: Database name (default: 'default')
- source_type: Data source type - clickhouse, postgresql, http, file (required)
- source_config: Source configuration dictionary (required)
- structure: List of column definitions with is_key flag (required)
- layout: Dictionary layout - flat, hashed, complex_key_hashed, cache, etc. (required)
- lifetime: TTL configuration with min/max (optional)
- description: Dictionary description (optional)

Generated: {{ _generated_at | default(now().isoformat()) }}
